WEBVTT

00:01:47.400 --> 00:01:47.959
Lord Hua

00:01:49.040 --> 00:01:50.120
Do you believe in fate?

00:01:51.319 --> 00:01:53.439
Fate is nothing but a delusion.

00:01:57.200 --> 00:01:58.280
Cause and effect are intertwined,

00:01:58.840 --> 00:02:00.840
like vines around a tree; the more you struggle, the tighter they bind.

00:02:01.519 --> 00:02:03.079
How do you know that birth, aging, sickness, and death

00:02:03.400 --> 00:02:04.640
are not the results of cause and effect?

00:02:09.360 --> 00:02:10.520
Cause and effect.

00:02:10.879 --> 00:02:12.039
Retribution.

00:02:34.039 --> 00:02:34.919
The rain is so heavy.

00:02:35.080 --> 00:02:35.680
Let's get inside, quick.

00:02:53.680 --> 00:02:54.400
When the rain stops,

00:02:55.039 --> 00:02:55.960
we can go home.

00:02:59.039 --> 00:03:00.520
My family is all gone.

00:03:01.960 --> 00:03:02.919
I have no home anymore.

00:03:04.919 --> 00:03:05.520
That's easy.

00:03:06.520 --> 00:03:07.520
Once we bow to heaven and earth,

00:03:08.319 --> 00:03:09.319
we will be a family.

00:03:10.319 --> 00:03:11.879
My home is your home.

00:03:12.759 --> 00:03:13.680
Then we can go home.

00:03:15.400 --> 00:03:15.919
Really?

00:03:19.599 --> 00:03:20.520
First bow to Heaven and Earth.

00:03:31.879 --> 00:03:33.080
Second bow to the parents.

00:03:59.719 --> 00:04:00.719
Husband and wife...

00:04:01.719 --> 00:04:02.680
Bow to each other.

00:04:57.120 --> 00:04:58.439
Thanks to the Crown Prince's aid,

00:04:59.079 --> 00:05:00.639
the treason case of Censor Chao Heng

00:05:00.759 --> 00:05:02.040
was thoroughly reinvestigated.

00:05:02.600 --> 00:05:04.000
The stigma the Chao family bore for years

00:05:04.000 --> 00:05:04.959
has finally been cleared.

00:05:05.839 --> 00:05:06.680
Time flies.

00:05:07.279 --> 00:05:08.360
One year later, the Emperor passed away.

00:05:08.680 --> 00:05:09.360
The new Emperor succeeded the throne.

00:05:10.000 --> 00:05:11.319
Nine Thousand Years committed numerous crimes.

00:05:11.600 --> 00:05:12.519
Punished for all crimes.

00:05:13.199 --> 00:05:15.279
Dali Temple arrested him by imperial decree.

00:05:15.920 --> 00:05:16.519
Justice

00:05:17.199 --> 00:05:18.079
has been served.

00:05:40.439 --> 00:05:43.319
Chaoyun, taste my newly brewed wine.

00:05:58.160 --> 00:05:59.240
Drinking without waiting for me again?

00:06:15.439 --> 00:06:16.199
How is this wine?

00:06:18.240 --> 00:06:18.839
Not bad.

00:06:20.560 --> 00:06:21.160
This past year,

00:06:21.720 --> 00:06:22.839
not serving at Dali Temple,

00:06:24.839 --> 00:06:25.600
how does it feel?

00:06:28.560 --> 00:06:30.560
How does it feel?

00:06:41.639 --> 00:06:42.279
Nine Thousand Years,

00:06:42.879 --> 00:06:43.879
today the new Emperor ascends the throne.

00:06:44.399 --> 00:06:45.279
He will surely settle past scores.

00:06:45.879 --> 00:06:46.720
You'd better lay low.

00:06:47.560 --> 00:06:48.439
What's the rush?

00:06:50.120 --> 00:06:51.839
Around the new Emperor, I have long since

00:06:51.839 --> 00:06:53.439
placed countless spies.

00:06:55.279 --> 00:06:57.439
Once the ascension ceremony concludes,

00:06:57.959 --> 00:07:00.800
the new Emperor will have become the late Emperor.

00:07:01.399 --> 00:07:03.279
When that time comes, my good nephew

00:07:04.000 --> 00:07:05.839
will naturally welcome me back to the palace.

00:07:06.959 --> 00:07:08.079
Nine Thousand Years is indeed

00:07:08.560 --> 00:07:09.959
so far-sighted.

00:07:23.240 --> 00:07:24.040
Madam Si,

00:07:25.000 --> 00:07:26.000
the great revenge is taken.

00:07:26.920 --> 00:07:27.680
You may rest in peace.

00:07:40.319 --> 00:07:41.000
Bring me another pot.

00:07:42.000 --> 00:07:42.319
Sure.

00:07:43.199 --> 00:07:43.920
I'll go get it for you.

00:08:07.879 --> 00:08:08.240
Master Kun,

00:08:10.000 --> 00:08:10.439
what is it?

00:09:29.440 --> 00:09:30.960
Where is the real Villa Master's daughter?

00:09:31.639 --> 00:09:35.480
Perhaps the Villa Master locked her elsewhere.

00:09:53.399 --> 00:09:54.440
He seems unable to speak.

00:10:44.360 --> 00:10:45.320
Put out the fire!

00:10:45.320 --> 00:10:46.000
Hurry!